HEADWORD: OAS
<hw>OAS</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The <org>Organization of American
States</org> an international association of countries in the Western
hemisphere. It was created in 1948 to promote military and economic and
social and cultural cooperation.</def> <mark>[acronym]</mark> ⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Organization of American States.</syn>⟦br⟧
